originalText: I'll sen' ye under fer dis!
::Pukes blood.:: I'll drown... ye... in... blood... fer... dis...
By d' sea, ye can hit...
Keep dat thin' away from me.
By d' sea, dat went in deep...
I don't like d'... d' freakin' col'...
I feel... it... in... me... bones...
By d' sea - I can't see! Aaaarghhh!
Where're ye, dumbat!? Yer fish chomp when I... when I...
Me dome's bein' crushed like a crab's shell!
::Grabs head.:: AAAARRGH! Me mind's gittin' banged up!
Git under, ye an' yer cross!
By d' sea... me vision's gittin' shaky...
I ain' goin' under... just yet...
Yer goin' down under... wit' me...
Ye... ain' poppin' me... ye ain'...
NOOOOO! Put it out, out - ow, ow!
Put it out! Aaaaaa! Put it out!
::Frantically tries to pat the fire out.::
By d' sea, can't move me legs!
I'm gunna sen' ye all under! Ha-ha-ha!
I'm gunna draw seas o' blood!
Oooh! It don' feel good in me head...
Gunna... uh, gunna pop d' stomach out...
No, by d' sea, leave me be!
I don' wanna die... Away wit' ye!
Don' pop me - I didn' loot nuthin'!
It hurts like a serpent's bite. ::Grabs chest.::
Ye leave me mind alone! AAAAAAA!
Gunna enjoy poppin' yer sorry ass.
I'm gunna bang ye up so hard yer momma ain' gunna recognize ye.
Ye'll regret ever messin' wit' me!
Fishes gunna love yer carcass, mhm!
Rub yer hands really fas'. Ha-ha!
Stay wit' me! Wan'cha to see what I'm gunna do to ye!
Yer eyes ain' lookin' right. Ha-ha!
Ye let dat woun' breathe... an' bleed!
Ye ain' good fer nuthin' but fish chomp.
By d' sea, I needed dis.
Yea... Ready to pop sum clods!
Yer brighter dan yer future, banga!
Let's see what you're made of!
Gunna bang ye up real good!
Gunna turn yer bones to powder!
Yea! Here's sum col' steel fer ye!
I like cuttin' up dumbats like ye!
By d' sea, nuthin' gunna be left of ye!
Gunna pour yer remains in the sea, banga!
Whatcha gunna do in d' dark?
I'll put dis thru yer dome!
Gunna pin ye to a wall, banga!
By d' sea, yer gittin' one between d' eyes!
Got a nice brain in yer dome...
Ye ain' safe in ther', banga!
Gunna turn yer brain to goo!
Ain' no one gunna dodge d' mind fist!
Wan' sum o' dem volts, banga?
Git ready! 'S frost bite fer ye!
Ye gunna be an icefoot, banga!
Mates gotta keep eachother cool, right?
Let's heat thin's up a bit...
I'm gunna dismantle ye, mech banga!
Gunna pull d' plug on ye!
Gunna fix me jet wit' yer bits!
We got sum clods to loot!
Seizin' d' momen' - an' sum loot!
Gunna chop yer ass into pieces!
Gunna split yer dome in half!
Gunna blow yer dome to bits, banga!
